				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">SMB should not scroll <em>at all</em> until Sprite-0 hit is detected.  When the frame starts drawing, it should be drawing from $2000 with <em>zero scroll changes</em>.  Until Sprite-0 is hit, at which point the game changes the scroll with $2000 and $2005 writes.</div>

