					<br /><b>Joined:</b> Wed Nov 10, 2004 6:47 pm<br /><b>Posts:</b> 1670
				</span>

			</td>
			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">To be technical -- you actually are supposed to use the <em>actual</em> PPU address (Loopy_V) for everything.  Loopy_T is only used to 'fill' Loopy_V at key times in the frame -- you should never use it directly.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

